synopsis.text: Climbing enthusiast Se-Heyon Choi finds herself in a complex situation when she discovers she is pregnant just before the World Championship. As a professional climber, she grapples with the reality of her impending motherhood, which threatens her long-held dreams. Meanwhile, she starts experiencing bizarre dreams of an alternate self, bound to a wheelchair and carrying a child. The line between reality and illusion blurs further when this alternate self begins sending her text messages from her own phone number. Caught in a whirlwind of confusion, Se-Heyon must navigate her aspirations, her unexpected pregnancy, and the enigmatic messages from a life that could have been hers.
